### Substantial Holder Notice (Form 603) Summary:  

- **Substantial Holder**: Australian Retirement Trust Pty Ltd ATF Australian Retirement Trust

- **Holding**: 25,600,011 fully paid ordinary shares (5.002% voting power)

- **Recent Activity**: Multiple buy/sell transactions from March-July 2025; net acquisition of ~1M shares on 03/07/2025 (AUD 2.69M).  

No other material information identified.
